fields.title: Skyrim
fields.content: The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim is an open-world action RPG set in the fantasy world of Tamriel, known for its vast world and rich lore.

fields.title: Mortal Kombat 11
fields.content: Mortal Kombat 11 is a fighting game that features brutal combat, fatalities, and a roster of iconic characters from the Mortal Kombat series.

fields.title: Fallout 4
fields.content: Fallout 4 is an open-world action RPG set in a post-apocalyptic wasteland, where players must navigate through the ruins of Boston and survive.

fields.title: Super Mario Odyssey
fields.content: Super Mario Odyssey is a platformer adventure game where Mario travels through various kingdoms with his new companion, Cappy, to save Princess Peach from Bowser's wedding plans.

fields.title: Doom Eternal
fields.content: Doom Eternal is a first-person shooter game where players take on the role of the Doom Slayer to battle against demonic forces from Hell.

fields.title: The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild
fields.content: The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild is an action-adventure game set in a vast open world where players can explore, solve puzzles, and battle enemies.

fields.title: Animal Crossing: New Horizons
fields.content: Animal Crossing: New Horizons is a life simulation game where players build and customize their own island paradise, interact with villagers, and more.

fields.title: League of Legends
fields.content: League of Legends is a multiplayer online battle arena game where players control characters known as champions and compete in fast-paced battles.

fields.title: Portal 2
fields.content: Portal 2 is a puzzle-platform game where players use a portal gun to create inter-spatial portals and solve challenging puzzles.

fields.title: Bloodborne
fields.content: Bloodborne is an action RPG set in the gothic city of Yharnam, where players hunt terrifying beasts and uncover dark secrets in a bid to end the nightmarish plague that grips the land.

fields.title: Persona 5
fields.content: Persona 5 is a role-playing game where players assume the role of a high school student who moonlights as a phantom thief, exploring dungeons, forming bonds, and battling supernatural enemies.

fields.title: Final Fantasy VII Remake
fields.content: Final Fantasy VII Remake is a reimagining of the classic RPG, following the story of Cloud Strife and his allies as they battle the megacorporation Shinra and confront the mysterious Sephiroth.

fields.title: The Last of Us Part II
fields.content: The Last of Us Part II is an action-adventure game that continues the story of Ellie and Joel in a post-apocalyptic world ravaged by the Cordyceps fungus infection, exploring themes of revenge and redemption.

fields.title: Hades
fields.content: Hades is a rogue-like action RPG where players control Zagreus, the son of Hades, as he attempts to escape the Underworld, battling through procedurally-generated dungeons and facing off against mythological foes.

fields.title: Celeste
fields.content: Celeste is a platformer game where players control Madeline as she climbs the titular Celeste Mountain, overcoming various obstacles and confronting her inner demons.

fields.title: Among Us
fields.content: Among Us is a multiplayer party game where players work together on a spaceship, completing tasks and identifying impostors among the crew before they sabotage the mission.

fields.title: Overwatch
fields.content: Overwatch is a team-based multiplayer first-person shooter game where players select from a roster of unique heroes, each with their own abilities, and work together to complete objectives.

fields.title: Stardew Valley
fields.content: Stardew Valley is a farming simulation game where players inherit a run-down farm and must restore it to its former glory, while also engaging in social activities, exploration, and dungeon crawling.

fields.title: Subnautica
fields.content: Subnautica is an open-world survival game set on an alien ocean planet, where players must explore the depths, gather resources, and craft equipment to survive against the planet's hostile fauna.

fields.title: Terraria
fields.content: Terraria is a sandbox adventure game where players explore, build, and fight in a procedurally-generated 2D world, encountering various enemies, bosses, and treasures.

fields.title: Minecraft
fields.content: Minecraft is a sandbox game where players can build, explore, and survive in a blocky, procedurally-generated world, gathering resources and crafting items to create their own adventures.
